  "title": "Infant Educarer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scopes</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Promote Feelings Of Security And Trust In Infants And Toddlers.</p>\n<p>2. Respond Positively To Infants And Toddlers’ Needs, Responses And Cues.</p>\n<p>3. Provide Routine Care Such As Bathing, Feeding, Diapering, Toileting, Dressing And Napping. Familiar With The Steps And Procedures In Carrying Out The Routine Care.</p>\n<p>4. Facilitate Children’s Exploratory Behavior, Thinking And Learning.</p>\n<p>5. Plan And Adapt Activities To Individual Child’s Needs.</p>\n<p>6. Communicate Effectively With Infants, Toddlers, Their Parents And Other Staff.</p>\n<p>7. Salary Depending On Experience And Qualification.</p>",
